h3 Fluid and Responsive
p.-text
  | Picker groups can be expanded to fill the parent space by applying the class <code>-fluid</code>.
  | By applying this class picker groups get stacked in smaller viewports.
h4 Horizontal
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--3
    .m-pickerGroup.-fluid
      each type in ['Radio1','Radio2','Radio3']
        input.a-picker(type="radio", name='radios', id=`id-${type}`)
        label(for=`id-${type}`)
          = type
